{"tid":988274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[已射]「中國製造」有多牛？英國建航母都離不開！","createTime":"2019-01-20T02:32:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T08:14:22.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"be3e33b0933dbe418d81df0c2e77a99ce57c2db1","tid":988274,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:32:14.000Z","msg":"「中國製造」有多牛？英國建航母都離不開！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20190118/29735850.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20190118%2F29735850.html&d=ugoaPMJGAUOlqu0hTQrapAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=7c900acd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20190118/29735850.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n參考消息網1月18日報導 台灣媒體報導，大陸官方以政策推動科技發展，研發各種新創科技外，也積極向全球輸出「中國製造」與「中國智造」，成果豐碩，除了抖音（TikTok）風靡全球年輕族群，成為2018年社交類APP下載冠軍之外，《王者榮耀》及其海外版《傳說對決》也以19.3億美元榮登全球最吸金手機遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《旺報》1月16日報導，除了社交娛樂方面的輸出之外，2018年，大陸遊客出境游達1.4億人次，蟬聯全球最大客源國，成為全球觀光界極力爭取的大戶，也因而帶動支付寶、微信支付全球普及速度。<br />\n<br />\n報導稱，已是大陸驕傲的高鐵運輸系統，輸出俄羅斯、巴西、秘魯。用於船舶生產、貨櫃運輸的大型門式起重機「龍門吊」，是大陸原創的重型機械，佔有全球90%市場，連英國也使用「龍門吊」才能製造航空母艦。<br />\n<br />\n報導稱，剛完成月球背面登陸任務的大陸航天局，已成為唯一持續不斷探索太空、研創新技術的單位，因此，歐洲太空總署把儲備航天員送到大陸航天局受訓；大陸自主研發北鬥射頻晶元可使用在手機等3C產品，以及衛星等大型高科技產品，已輸出全球90餘個國家和地區，銷量突破7000萬片。"},{"pid":"2557c1ce13fe63653fca5101c14711bd9dc86dda","tid":988274,"uid":55868,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:36:07.000Z","msg":"dllm,  仲以前咩高科技產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b4b77df60b74ff7fd39072b868746e1c635b66","tid":988274,"uid":55868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2557c1ce13fe63653fca5101c14711bd9dc86dda","tid":988274,"uid":55868,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:36:07.000Z","msg":"dllm,  仲以前咩高科技產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:36:19.000Z","msg":"以為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e610023419688a5713402a227092d3713c2bd77","tid":988274,"uid":70786,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:42:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">大陸遊客出境游達1.4億人次，蟬聯全球最大客源國，成為全球觀光界極力爭取的大戶</span><br />\n支那人個名臭晒都可以打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">連英國也使用「龍門吊」才能製造航空母艦。</span><br />\n為人作嫁衣裳當正自己嫁得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4b167917b5394c00d411435f0b3198c66cb254","tid":988274,"uid":24570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:43:14.000Z","msg":"多牛？"},{"pid":"627da46620eb5d01a7961b709a0d47c8701a9cc1","tid":988274,"uid":52942,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:44:36.000Z","msg":"牛？睇過？邊撚度牛呀？而家冇人識你呀！而家熊呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6937127d4893353900454bc4539edc63bcb3f871","tid":988274,"uid":3423,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:45:51.000Z","msg":"嗰龍門吊是HlT設計的"},{"pid":"4c1c3997c5407cb5c707dcc3dfd02e01363c1f81","tid":988274,"uid":5020,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:46:00.000Z","msg":"龍門吊幾時變咗大陸發明？"},{"pid":"c4c6fa433bb12a39f918f2a8c051e6d3f307e0d7","tid":988274,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:48:30.000Z","msg":"唔買你咪買第二間<br />\n頂多咪貴d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af86866262f73377dc066fbc077ce6b1b69d32d","tid":988274,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6937127d4893353900454bc4539edc63bcb3f871","tid":988274,"uid":3423,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:45:51.000Z","msg":"嗰龍門吊是HlT設計的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:49:08.000Z","msg":"用人設計當自主研發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77af180da709dfa4559e98f613